{"tid":888161,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"美國總統“Game of Thrones”式Twitter引來HBO反對","createTime":"2018-11-03T13:35:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T13:41:24.000Z","uid":202966,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"885685374e9929e2b2cf9e017e898772e868a6b2","tid":888161,"uid":202966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T13:35:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.careerengine.us/api/aov2/https%3A_%7C__%7C_mmbiz.qpic.cn_%7C_mmbiz_jpg_%7C_ky7WP9dG2sZJDFhkKFR1XE4vnAia41teTvh4bcO1PVkQydAI2IDUhr7ZW65sqXLrn8pFt71VVu6Lob3yqbIxLoA_%7C_640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.careerengine.us%2Fapi%2Faov2%2Fhttps%253A_%257C__%257C_mmbiz.qpic.cn_%257C_mmbiz_jpg_%257C_ky7WP9dG2sZJDFhkKFR1XE4vnAia41teTvh4bcO1PVkQydAI2IDUhr7ZW65sqXLrn8pFt71VVu6Lob3yqbIxLoA_%257C_640%253Fwx_fmt%253Djpeg&h=63c4e07a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國現任總統當勞&middot;特朗普（Donald Trump）日前在Twitter上的一則更新迎來不少爭議，特別是HBO。 <br />\n<br />\n在這則更新中，他分享了一張自己的照片並配文&ldquo;制裁即將來臨&rdquo;（Sanctions are Coming）以及日期&ldquo;11月5日&rdquo;。其實美國總統當勞&middot;特朗普在推文中要傳達的信息是美方將從11/5開始對伊朗重啟經濟制裁，這原本沒什麼，但問題在於其字體和風格都讓人不禁聯想到HBO的&ldquo;王牌劇&rdquo;《權力的遊戲》（Game of Thrones）。<br />\n<br />\n劇迷們都知道&ldquo;凜冬將至&rdquo;（Winter is Coming）是用來宣傳該劇的標語，而HBO第一時間對此做出瞭如下回應：&ldquo;我們之前對這並不知情並希望我們的商標不要被用於政治意圖&rdquo;。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.careerengine.us/api/aov2/https%3A_%7C__%7C_mmbiz.qpic.cn_%7C_mmbiz_jpg_%7C_ky7WP9dG2sZJDFhkKFR1XE4vnAia41teTYmzApxzpmD70MfmNVwU8v5rIq0kbSHxeftbq46fBw3cVZtZebegQag_%7C_640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.careerengine.us%2Fapi%2Faov2%2Fhttps%253A_%257C__%257C_mmbiz.qpic.cn_%257C_mmbiz_jpg_%257C_ky7WP9dG2sZJDFhkKFR1XE4vnAia41teTYmzApxzpmD70MfmNVwU8v5rIq0kbSHxeftbq46fBw3cVZtZebegQag_%257C_640%253Fwx_fmt%253Djpeg&h=7f8a5c17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《Game of Thrones》最終季（共6集）確定2019年回歸。新一季的導演陣容包括戴維&middot;貝尼奧夫（David Benioff）、D&middot;B&middot;威斯（DB Weiss）、大衛&middot;努特爾（David Nutter）和米格爾&middot;薩普什尼克（Miguel Sapochnik）；參與編劇的則有戴維&middot;貝尼奧夫、D&middot;B&middot;威斯、布萊恩&middot;考格曼（Bryan Cogman）和Dave Hill。"},{"pid":"1256b0024919ea76c4f1258b315153b3b3ba6389","tid":888161,"uid":43231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T13:40:04.000Z","msg":"得六集<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad9d78d49b55a0beb0c753a2c2862c7462edee82","tid":888161,"uid":202966,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T13:41:24.000Z","msg":"Game of Thrones <br />\nWestworld <br />\nBig Little Lies <br />\nVeep <br />\nSilicon Valley <br />\nTrue Detective <br />\n呢d show全部慘了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}